{
  "stem": "7160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day-- one day my father went to open the business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He find on the door a piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What it says in German, it says, while anybody will remove this paper, they will be executed on the spot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, they went there, they become owners of my father's property.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took everything-- what's inside the store, and they ship it to Germany-- every up to the last nail.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had no business, and we have to struggle, you know, to survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and from there after-- after a while, they start taking the young people to work for the Germans, to make roads.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And were-- we forced-- forced slave labor to make roads and different things for the German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We're working about a year for them, probably a little longer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "People start dying from typhus and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was mistreating, beating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And finally, the Jewish community-- it was quite a few of wealthy people-- they offer a large amount of money to the Germans to release us, you know, from this slavery.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So-- then they release.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a few months later, they lock us in ghettos, because we were living in sections of Jewish neighborhoods together.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I got locked in my-- in my-- my neighborhood, it was about 10,000 Jews-- and where I was born and grew up there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they lock us up in terror.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "After a-- after a few months later, they start taking and shipping-- they taking people, start sending to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We don't know at the time where we was going to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They told us a lie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was a repossessing a different place till the war ends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they took everything we had.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
